            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is a very famous school in Gurugram. It was First established in New Delhi in 1949. It's a very prestigious school of New Delhi. Due to its name and fame demand for the DPS was increased and the management took initiative to establish more branches in New Delhi and now it has become a Pan India school. The school in Gurugram has seats for +3 yrs children. Has an elegant building right on main Golf Course Extension Road. The school has it's own bus fleets for its students. Security of junior classes is tight with numerous security staff. Expenditure of Education is on higher side as school provides clean environment for its students. Teaching staff is humble and of the standard of any international school.",
